      <h1>About Gilead Couriers</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Gilead Couriers provides a discreet, reliability-first A-to-B courier service across the UK for clients who cannot
        afford delays, ambiguity, or poor handling.
      </p>

      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <p>
        We deliver time-critical consignments directly from pickup to drop-off — with professional communication and clear confirmation.
        Typical jobs include urgent parts, sensitive documents, high-value items, and scheduled A-to-B movements.
      </p>

      <h2>Who we support</h2>
      <p>
        Our service is designed for high-trust environments, including professional and regulated contexts such as engineering,
        manufacturing, legal services, healthcare suppliers, and government-adjacent organisations — as well as private clients with
        sensitive or high-value requirements.
      </p>

      <h2>How we operate</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Direct A-to-B</strong> — no unnecessary stops, no “multi-drop” uncertainty.</li>
        <li><strong>Discretion</strong> — sensitive handling and professional conduct.</li>
        <li><strong>Reliability</strong> — clear confirmation and accountable delivery.</li>
        <li><strong>Communication</strong> — booking confirmation and dispatch updates.</li>
      </ul>

